9. Nb5 Nf5 10. Qxd8+ Kxd8 11. Ng5 Nh6 12. dxc5 bxc5 $11) 7... c5 $5 $146 {
The same issue as above.} 8. Bf2 Nf5 9. Nf3 Nc6 10. O-O-O (10. Bb5 Bd7 11.
