23. exf6 Ne8 24. f4 $14) 22. exf6 Ne8 {It is best to retrieve the pawn with
the knight, as else it would remain passive on g7.} (22... Rf8 23. Qf4 Qxf4 24.
Nxf4 Rxf6 25. Nd3 $14) 23. Qg3 Nf7 $11 {Followed by ...Qxf6 without running
into any fork.} *

