{[#]White answered 20...Nxe3 with 21.Nc5. The queen is in danger but there are
at least two ways to get reasonable compensation for it. How} 21... Ng4 $5 (
21... Bxc5 $5 22. b3 Qf1+ $3 (22... Be7 $2 {didn't offer Black enough
compensation for the material.} 23. bxc4 Nxc4 24. Qc2 $16 {Chesney,B-Gulko,B 
