and the king will be in danger.} 24. Nd3 Bxd3 25. Qxd3 Nxf2 26. Qa6+ Kd7 27.
Kf1 Ng4 28. g3 (28. h3 Ne3+ 29. Rxe3 Bxe3 30. g3 d4) 28... Nxh2+ 29. Kg2 Ng4 {
with very unclear play in both lines.} *

