{[#]Black has just blocked the centre with 8...c4, answered by Bd3-f1. How did
he plan to continue his queenside play?} 9... b5 $1 {[%cal Ga7a5] Immobilizing
the b4-pawn in order to prepare ...a7-a5.} (9... a5 10. b5 $16 {leaves Black
with little breathing space for his minor pieces.}) 10. g3 (10. Nxb5 a5 $1 $11
